# Servly UI Agent Notes

This repository is the umbrella catalog and future aggregation layer for independently owned Servly UI components.

## Ownership

- Do not place component implementation source in this repository before a real shared composition layer exists.
- Each component repository owns its code, tests, documentation playground, package build, and npm release.
- Link component repositories and npm packages from the root README instead of duplicating source or adding Git submodules.
- Keep this repository private from npm until it exports an intentional aggregation API.
- Do not modify `/Users/eddiesosera/Documents/Dev/Servly/noPrompt-portal` unless the user explicitly requests portal integration.

## Current Components

- `ServlyNumberInput`: https://github.com/servlyapp/servly-number-input
- `@servlyui/number-input`: https://www.npmjs.com/package/@servlyui/number-input

## Future Aggregation

Add workspace tooling only when at least two components require shared documentation, testing, tokens, or composition. Shared abstractions must have a concrete cross-component use case.
